## Guardrails
- Never enter a contract with less than EXPIRY_AVOIDANCE_MIN minutes remaining
- Always close the current position before transitioning to a new contract
- If no contract meets liquidity criteria, log "NO_ELIGIBLE_CONTRACT" and skip — do not force a trade
- Validate contract ticker against Kalshi API before submitting any order — tickers expire
- Contract selection must re-run on every candle close — do not cache the selected contract across candles
